# Negative Constraints

## NEVER

- NEVER use `document.getElementById` — use React refs
- NEVER import from `src/` — use package imports
- NEVER add inline styles — use CSS modules or className

## DO NOT

- DO NOT suggest class components — only functional + hooks
- DO NOT suggest `any` type — always provide proper types
- DO NOT modify test snapshots manually — regenerate them

## AVOID

- AVOID deep nesting (max 3 levels)
- AVOID barrel exports (index.ts re-exports)
- AVOID default exports — use named exports

## How to verify

1. `rg -n "document\.getElementById" <changed-files>` — zero results.
2. `rg -n "from ['\"]src/" <changed-files>` — zero results.
3. `rg -n ": any" <changed-files>` — zero results.
4. `rg -n "export default" <changed-files>` — zero results.
5. `rg -n "style=" <changed-files>` — zero inline styles in JSX.
